sequenceDiagram
    participant Zoom
    participant RTMS
    participant EventPub
    participant TalkTime
    participant Redis
    participant PostgreSQL
    participant API
    participant UI

    Zoom->>RTMS: Audio/Video Stream
    RTMS->>EventPub: Stream Events
    EventPub->>TalkTime: Subscribe to Events
    
    loop Every Event
        TalkTime->>TalkTime: Calculate Metrics
        TalkTime->>Redis: Cache Real-time Data
        TalkTime->>PostgreSQL: Store Aggregated Data
    end
    
    UI->>API: Request Analytics
    API->>Redis: Get Real-time Metrics
    API->>PostgreSQL: Get Historical Data
    API->>UI: Return Combined Data
    UI->>UI: Display Dashboard